        dc:description           "Figure L 14. Labels. i Bulimus confluens Pfeiffer, 1855 ii Bulimus confusus Reeve, 1848 iii Drymaeus conicus da Costa, 1907 iv Bulimus convexus Pfeiffer, 1855 v Helix cora d'Orbigny, 1835 vi Helix crepundia d'Orbigny, 1835." , "Figure 58. Neopetraeus species. A-B Neopetraeus cora (d'Orbigny, 1835), lectotype NHMUK 1854.12.4.124 (H = 43.9) C-E Neopetraeus binneyanus (Pfeiffer, 1857), lectotype NHMUK 1975426 (H = 25.2) F-G Neopetraeus excoriatus (Pfeiffer, 1855), lectotype NHMUK 1975500 (H = 38.4). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26765" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26730" .

